// ============================================================
// Operational Excellence Survey — response data (Oct 2025)
// ============================================================
// Anonymous open-ended responses from the University of Idaho
// Operational Excellence survey (Strategic Plan Pillar 5).
// Faculty/staff: 113 respondents. Students: 54 respondents.
//
// PROVENANCE: extracted once from the two Microsoft Forms exports
// (a one-time ingest, not regenerated on build). The survey was
// anonymous (no names/emails collected). Before publication a
// naming scan de-identified individuals named in free text:
//   - 7 responses had personal names replaced with role descriptors
//     (shown in [brackets]); one self-signature was removed.
//   - 2 responses were withheld entirely from the public view
//     (one named a leader with personal criticism; one was charged
//     political content naming specific campus programs).
// This file is the source of truth going forward; edit here to
// correct a verbatim (it is not regenerated on build).
// ============================================================

